if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_7();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != '405014cd1bcd63ce977f32739a54865fc3f6c6d1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '405014cd1bcd63ce977f32739a54865fc3f6c6d1') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'c25608ef2c618e7eedc0268d87958c2b95e67834') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_7();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '405014cd1bcd63ce977f32739a54865fc3f6c6d1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/test_database_plugins')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/test_database_plugins');
	writefile_8();
	if (!is_file('dev/test_database_plugins')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/test_database_plugins');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') != 'f3c176893b9c3c48e5d322468f6d48c36baac019') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/test_database_plugins');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/test_database_plugins', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/test_database_plugins');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') !== 'f3c176893b9c3c48e5d322468f6d48c36baac019') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') !== '8ca1b3f5158fae16f682bd845298f01cd5601602') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/test_database_plugins');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/test_database_plugins');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/test_database_plugins')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/test_database_plugins', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_8();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') !== 'f3c176893b9c3c48e5d322468f6d48c36baac019') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/test_database_plugins');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('bmRlZD0wO3doaXRlU3BhY2U9d3JhcDtodG1sPTE7Zm9udFNpemU9MzA7ZmlsbENvbG9yPSNmOGNlY2M7c3Ryb2tlQ29sb3I9I2I4NTQ1MDtzaGFkb3c9MDsiIHBhcmVudD0iMSIgdmVydGV4PSIxIj4KICAgICAgICAgIDxteEdlb21ldHJ5IHg9IjEzNzAiIHk9IjQ4'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('MCIgd2lkdGg9IjE4MCIgaGVpZ2h0PSI1MCIgYXM9Imdlb21ldHJ5IiAvPgogICAgICAgIDwvbXhDZWxsPgogICAgICA8L3Jvb3Q+CiAgICA8L214R3JhcGhNb2RlbD4KICA8L2RpYWdyYW0+CjwvbXhmaWxlPgo='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
	writefile_9();
	if (!is_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio') != '556d58db95c57335b2abc29a48c0a441ac6ba17a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio') !== '556d58db95c57335b2abc29a48c0a441ac6ba17a') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio') !== '2284289c390c57f3aa62e2ae92dbc40b7b511d37') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_9();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio') !== '556d58db95c57335b2abc29a48c0a441ac6ba17a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png') != '07d7061cfd8028913c709eca907d5b9be5e02e6a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png') !== '07d7061cfd8028913c709eca907d5b9be5e02e6a') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png') !== '71038c2c5dd32774957fa1db1d295de27aea9f54') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png') !== '07d7061cfd8028913c709eca907d5b9be5e02e6a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt');
	writefile_11();
	if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt') != '52e4238cb23efc035ca151e6bbf1cf66589a07d8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt') !== '52e4238cb23efc035ca151e6bbf1cf66589a07d8') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt') !== '6aafb0495962d50106fc822ac8696b04a9b7c587') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt') !== '52e4238cb23efc035ca151e6bbf1cf66589a07d8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/database/oracle_test_vm.txt');
		}
	}
}

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/install_alpine_linux.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/install_alpine_linux.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_12();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/install_alpine_linux.md') !== '7d1b7e4967416121fca434bc0d3e37483c2af44e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/install_alpine_linux.md');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php') != '59f78fbe763617ed8a68aade74a93a63b0f78d2f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php') !== '59f78fbe763617ed8a68aade74a93a63b0f78d2f') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php') !== '9a7ee39d5ca4b9ca5beb2c230ee0c55294e824ca') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php') !== '59f78fbe763617ed8a68aade74a93a63b0f78d2f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php') !== '11978248af7acc1b2734a235ca8c8371865e86cc') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php') !== '920e33802acdef316129bb40cb7bf556d852a8cd') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_21();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php') !== '11978248af7acc1b2734a235ca8c8371865e86cc') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
		}
	}

if (!is_file('includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php');
	writefile_23();
	if (!is_file('includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php') != 'eb69d6702ba70a8bf92f99d86944c899e8e18f27') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php') !== 'eb69d6702ba70a8bf92f99d86944c899e8e18f27') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php') !== 'd9369c3e4594f7de7dc1c3cee91281c0a4dc9e6b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_23();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php') !== 'eb69d6702ba70a8bf92f99d86944c899e8e18f27') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update205.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/functions.inc.php');
	writefile_24();
	if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') != '12b2b2ef101bdabd132daaae8a0cf1825c58f242') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/functions.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/functions.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '12b2b2ef101bdabd132daaae8a0cf1825c58f242') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '05ff4724d4299f928bcfa88efb27a34679362b3c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/functions.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/functions.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/functions.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/functions.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_24();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '12b2b2ef101bdabd132daaae8a0cf1825c58f242') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js');
	writefile_29();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js') != '6278f6a5d4ed742d37da89f43b3d3a1b32276f67') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js') !== '6278f6a5d4ed742d37da89f43b3d3a1b32276f67') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js') !== '1e12ba02d88bfadf2019e4692259bb1b980261c3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_29();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js') !== '6278f6a5d4ed742d37da89f43b3d3a1b32276f67') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/oci/OIDplusDatabasePluginOciSetup.js');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js');
	writefile_31();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js') != '4bfdee6de319756f015bf822ff1f5a9cc856d7fc') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js') !== '4bfdee6de319756f015bf822ff1f5a9cc856d7fc') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js') !== '179386df0e1808774ea89c67abdf9154f1c87d22') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_31();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js') !== '4bfdee6de319756f015bf822ff1f5a9cc856d7fc') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBCSetup.js');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js');
	writefile_35();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js') != '24d852631d71783ab1811aec732dcbc2b1c1e538') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js') !== '24d852631d71783ab1811aec732dcbc2b1c1e538') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js') !== '22b451fb1b783f8d3c4a876fab6a5cffb04c0684') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_35();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js') !== '24d852631d71783ab1811aec732dcbc2b1c1e538') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/OIDplusDatabasePluginPgSqlSetup.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_38();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != 'a494db9fef5ce3c69da208770b7391369c8bad99') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'a494db9fef5ce3c69da208770b7391369c8bad99') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '9a761fa824d3b76ba5c26be6ac33be7b1149f734') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_38();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'a494db9fef5ce3c69da208770b7391369c8bad99') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}
